snippet.title: Stuntfest - World Tour | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Ready, set, EJECT!

Grab your car and dive right into the crazy action circus of Stuntfest - World Tour! Race, wreck and bounce with up to 18 players in an elimination-based tournament. Show off your spectacular tricks and be the best of the fest.

Stuntfest – World Tour is coming to PC later this year.

Trailer footage is from the pre-alpha version of Stuntfest World Tour.

- Links & Info -
Steam: https://thqn.net/stunt-steam
Website: http://stuntfestgame.com
Discord: http://discord.gg/stuntfest

- Our Socials -
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCt3ISe3XarnrTiWUt9PJm_w
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Stuntfest
